- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning a visual representation for e-commerce products and image retrieval. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with fashion images and their representation. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses image retrieval tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses weakly supervised learning to train the model. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with label prediction for clothing categories.
